where ƒ is the frequency, ξ is a constant without physical meaning. As shown in Fig. 4b, the fitted Ed is 0.017 eV. To further confirm defect depth obtained with AS, we measured the temperature dependent dark I–V curves from 80 to 320 K (Additional file 1: Fig. S18) and calculated defect depth Ea by Eq. (7) [54].7σ=σ0exp-EakBT,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
